Package edu.byu.cs.superasteroids.model_classes.visible_objects

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Asteroid
    Created by Marshall Garey This class is a container for info about an asteroid and is a superclass for the various types of asteroids.
    BgObject
    Created by Marshall Garey Information about a background object in the game, such as nebulas, etc.
    GrowingAsteroid
    Created by Marshall Garey Growing asteroids continuously get bigger until they reach the maximum size.
    MiniMap
    Created by Marshall Garey The mini-map is always in the same place on the user's viewport.
    MovingObject
    Created by Marshall Garey This class contains information and methods common to all moving objects.
    Octeroid
    Created by Marshall Garey Octeroids split into 8 pieces when they are destroyed.
    PositionedObject
    Created by Marshall Garey These objects have a position (x and y coordinates) in the universe/world.
    Projectile
    Created by Marshall Garey This class has information about the projectiles that the ship's cannon shoots.
    Ship
    Created by Marshall Garey The class has all the information about the ship that the player is flying.
    Space
    Created by Marshall Garey The background for the world, or universe, or outer space.
    Viewport
    Created by Marshall Garey The currently visible rectangular portion of the world
    VisibleObject
    Created by Marshall Garey Visible objects are things that the user can see.
